OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOscars to use crisis team  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fafter Will Smith slap      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A "crisis team" will be introduced at  
OL,6, this year's Oscars, to handle any      
OL,7, real-time incidents as a response to   
OL,8, Will Smith slapping Chris Rock during  
OL,9, the 2022 ceremony.                     
OL,11,FAcademy chief executive Bill Kramer    
OL,12,Ftold Time magazine the new unit had    
OL,13,F"run many scenarios" in the hope they  
OL,14,Fwill be "prepared for anything".       
OL,16,F"Because of last year, we've opened our
OL,17,Fminds to the many things that can      
OL,18,Fhappen at the Oscars," he said.        
OL,20,FThey are now quicker to react, he said.
